name: yushuang
description:
a realistic LORA model for yushuang, a LPL host,

her smile, grin, mouth opening for chilloutmix

used in forms of full portrait,three quarters portrait, or close-up shot

0.7-0.8 weights will be fine,

it might includes many watermarks from training images set, which means you need to offset by adding appropriate negative prompt

余霜的真实LORA模型，

可以生成露齿笑，微笑，微微张嘴

全身，半身，特写

权重大概0.7-0.8

生成的图片需要特别地用去水印的负面tag来抵消，这是我制作训练图片时遗留下来的错误
